nodes.text: A B1 battle droid was stationed on the planet Felucia during the events of the Second Battle of Felucia

During the Battle of Felucia around 21 BBY, this B1-Series battle droid was under command of T-series tactical droid TZ-33 in a Separatist outpost. When a team of clone troopers lead by Jedi generals Plo Koon and Anakin Skywalker and commander Ahsoka Tano arrived on the planet to take down the Separatist stronghold, this droid informed TZ-33 of their presence and was ordered later on to lower the gate of the facility to allow the droids inside to form up for a counter-attack.
This B1 battle droid, like every battle droid in The Clone Wars movie and The Clone Wars TV series, was voiced by Matthew Wood. His name was never given.
